# Vault Password File Template
# 
# 1. Copy this file to .vault_pass
# 2. Replace 'your_vault_password_here' with your actual vault password
# 3. Make sure .vault_pass has restricted permissions (chmod 600 on Linux/Mac)
# 4. Add .vault_pass to .gitignore to prevent accidental commits
#
# Example:
# your_vault_password_here
#
# Usage:
# ansible-playbook --vault-password-file .vault_pass -i inventory playbook.yml
